    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Thanks for the report. Pls use `loc`:\n\n```\ndf.loc['row3', 'col1'] = 2\ndf\n#       col1  col2  col3\n# row1     0     0     0\n# row2     0     0     0\n# row3     2   NaN   NaN\n```\n\nI think it should raise `SettingWithCopyWarning`. \n"
